mstItem.name: Cursed Beast Gallstone
mstItem.detail:
"Skill Up & Ascension Material"
A stone whose curse fermented in the innards of a hexed beast.
It continues to release a strong curse that will never fade.

mstItem.name: Mystic Spinal Fluid
mstItem.detail:
"Skill Up & Ascension Material"
A potion to turn an ordinary human into a mage. When injected into the spine, it creates temporary artificial Magical Circuits.

mstItem.name: Secret Gem of Archer
mstItem.detail:
"Skill Up Material"
A bright stone glimmering with the immense power of an Archer.

mstItem.name: Stake of Wailing Night
mstItem.detail:
"Skill Up & Ascension Material"
A stake driven into a corpse to prevent its reanimation.
It never rusts, and retains its luster by absorbing blood.
It can even pierce otherworldly beings that lurk in the dark of night.

mstItem.name: Void's Dust
mstItem.detail:
"Skill Up & Ascension Material"
Dust that disperses when hollow shadows disappear.

mstItem.name: Arrowhead of Malice
mstItem.detail:
"Skill Up & Ascension Material"
An arrowhead that has bathed in blood, sin, and corruption. It is said to carry a curse that invites disaster.

mstItem.name: Servant Coin
mstItem.detail:
"Servant Enhancement Material"
 A shard of a Servant's Spirit Origin

mstItem.name: Gem of Archer
mstItem.detail:
"Skill Up Material"
A bright stone glimmering with the power of an Archer.

mstItem.name: Evil Bone
mstItem.detail:
"Skill Up & Ascension Material"
Ominous bones wielding curses.

mstItem.name: Magic Gem of Archer
mstItem.detail:
"Skill Up Material"
A bright stone glimmering with the great power of an Archer.

mstItem.name: Crystallized Lore
mstItem.detail:
"Skill Up & Ascension Material"
A highly pure crystal of magic created
when human history crosses a stream of Mana.
It can be said that it is the ingredient for materializing Heroic Spirits.

mstItem.name: Tearstone of Blood
mstItem.detail:
"Skill Up & Ascension Material"
The crystal of the tear shed by a giant eyeball-like creature when it dies.
A strong curse is residing within this crystal.

mstItem.name: Scale of Fantasy
mstItem.detail:
"Skill Up & Ascension Material"
Scales shed from fairy wings.
They serve as a reagent for various magical powders.

mstItem.name: Archer Piece
mstItem.detail:
"Ascension Material"
A piece signifying the Archer class.

mstItem.name: Archer Monument
mstItem.detail:
"Ascension Material"
A monument in glory of the Archer class.

mstItem.name: Holy Grail
mstItem.detail:
A container said to grant any wish.
Created by the Third Magic, it is said 
that it can materialize those that do not possess forms.
